title: Skylar Schneider and Alfredo Rodriguez win American Criterium Cup race at the Tour of America’s Dairyland
content:
Alfredo Rodriguez and Andrea Cyr lead the overall series, while Kim Lucie and Danny Summerhill retain the sprint lead after race four. 

Read the full article at Skylar Schneider and Alfredo Rodriguez win American Criterium Cup race at the Tour of America’s Dairyland on Velo.
author: Will Tracy
